171 A.3d 1258 VINCENT INNARELLA, PLAINTIFF-PETITIONER, v. WEDGEWOOD CONDOMINIUM ASSOCIATES, INC., WEDGEWOOD GARDEN CONDO ASSOCIATION, INC., PROGRESSIVE BUILDING MANAGEMENT COMPANY, INC., GARDEN HOMES, INC., THE PROGRESSIVE COMPANIES, AND LAKEVIEW GARDENS, DEFENDANTS-RESPONDENTS.

C-203 Sept. Term 2017

079694 October 20, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002542-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
